transforms.name: vite:vue
transforms.result:
.site-footer
		.logo-wrapper
			.divider
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)
				flex: 1

				@media (min-width: $md)
					&:first-child
						flex: 0
						flex-basis: 15%

					&:last-child
						flex: 1

		.footer-columns
			.col:nth-child(1),
			.col:nth-child(2)
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)
				margin-bottom: 2rem

				@media (min-width: $md)
					margin: 0
					border: 0
					border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)

		.btn-gradient
			width: 50%

			.btn-image
				margin: 0
				min-width: 60px
				text-align: center

				img
					width: 45px

			.btn-text
				flex: 1

			@media (min-width: $sm)
				width: 100px !important

	.btn-terms
		white-space: break-spaces !important

	.footer-copy a
		color: white
